query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS vehicle_number_records (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  parkingLotId INT NOT NULL,
  area VARCHAR(20),
  classNumber VARCHAR(10),
  kana VARCHAR(5),
  digits VARCHAR(10),
  fullNumber VARCHAR(50),
  plateType VARCHAR(20),
  plateUse VARCHAR(20),
  plateColor VARCHAR(10),
  imageUrl TEXT,
  recognitionSuccess BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
  rawResponse TEXT,
  capturedAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (parkingLotId) REFERENCES parking_lots(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS camera_settings (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  parkingLotId INT NOT NULL,
  cameraName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  cameraType VARCHAR(50),
  ipAddress VARCHAR(45),
  port INT DEFAULT 80,
  username VARCHAR(100),
  password VARCHAR(256),
  snapshotPath VARCHAR(256),
  captureIntervalMinutes INT DEFAULT 60 NOT NULL,
  enabled BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE NOT NULL,
  lastCaptureAt BIGINT,
  lprApiToken VARCHAR(256),
  lprApiUrl VARCHAR(256),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (parkingLotId) REFERENCES parking_lots(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
